ji\" />"},{"pid":"b84fe9c6b342718fbb7700e06dc6a038476b7e8a","tid":153140,"uid":49293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"慣左 快好多"},{"pid":"e7e84e5eb20c2ab4a404b2085f5e704f19c32416","tid":153140,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"成個小學雞咁"},{"pid":"083913e853c0969ed8c944022454920d76639698","tid":153140,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"上不嬲都2級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落有時都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落好似會有離心力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1677bb0d42add53b080d57a16d130293091c899f","tid":153140,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔覺有咩問題<br />\n好似慳力少少</blockquote><br />\n力我就唔覺得慳既<br />\n反而用力會多左，一級一級慢慢咁上會舒服啲，但真係咁多年習慣左好難一下子改到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n力係會有慳到<br />\n之前電視有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caa105c8b6bfdb3895b24dbf2a55cefa701ba71","tid":153140,"uid":45352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上不嬲都2級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落有時都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落好似會有離心力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果果下係落地面就會幾級跳囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果你話成條樓梯都兩級兩級咁落就咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一個唔覺意差錯腳就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6288b8bfd0da21a2e042e7fab525f302807c30b","tid":153140,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔覺有咩問題<br />\n好似慳力少少</blockquote><br />\n力我就唔覺得慳既<br />\n反而用力會多左，一級一級慢慢咁上會舒服啲，但真係咁多年習慣左好難一下子改到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n力係會有慳到<br />\n之前電視有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔襤就會腳尖落地 <br />\n行幾層小腿脹晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ef766b13b5b77fdeb2c0cbb9ff3b9f0a219ebc","tid":153140,"uid":47722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"慣左襤級上同落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}